OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FLargely dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Perhaps some outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Freaching western hills late in the
OL,9,Fday. Breezier, but still feeling warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FEarly
OL,12,Frain clearing to brighter and fresher
OL,13,Fconditions with scattered showers
OL,14,FSunday. Breezy with sunny spells and
OL,15,Fscattered showers Monday. Further
OL,16,Fscattered showers Tuesday. Feeling
OL,17,Fmuch fresher than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
